summary: The two most famous RS (Runescape) Gods join the fray, Saradomin and Zamorak have come to help the Dovahkiin defeat Alduin and protect the land of Tamriel.
descriptionHtml:
WARNING: INCREDIBLY OVERPOWERED, AND ESSENTIAL, USE AT YOUR OWN RISK.

This adds the two most famous Runescape Gods of all time to your game, Saradomin and Zamorak.

Opening a portal from Gielinor to this foreign world of Tamriel, and ready to join the DragonBorn on his quest, should they be found.

Ah yes, I did not stutter, in order for them to join you, you must find them, and only then will they decide to join you.
author: Darskul
